###### This is an &lt;h6&gt; tag</pre>
              <p><strong>Text styles</strong></p>
              <pre>*This text will be italic*
_This will also be italic_
**This text will be bold**
__This will also be bold__

*You **can** combine them*</pre>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
              <h2>Lists</h2>
              <p><strong>Unordered</strong></p>
              <pre>* Item 1
* Item 2
  * Item 2a
  * Item 2b</pre>
              <p><strong>Ordered</strong></p>
              <pre>1. Item 1
2. Item 2
3. Item 3
   * Item 3a
   * Item 3b</pre>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
              <h2>Miscellaneous</h2>
